room_title: Escape room "Superheroes Adventure" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: This was our second time going to this escape room experience. Olivia was our game master both times (Super Hero Room and Japanese thriller), and she does such a great job directing us when we needed a hint. She definitely adds to the experience with her bubbly attitude!

room_title: Escape room "Superheroes Adventure" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: Adam was awesome! Loved the superhero room. Liked the addition of superhero powers. Definitely come here and try it out!

room_title: Escape room "Superheroes Adventure" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: We had a great time doing two rooms. The Japanese Thriller Room and Super Hero room. Even though we weren't successful, we had a great time working with Gill and making new friends for the night. Great concepts.
